  <text x="50" y="386" dominant-baseline="central" style="fill:rgb(61, 61, 58);stroke:none;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);stroke-width:1px;stroke-linecap:butt;stroke-linejoin:miter;opacity:1;font-family:&quot;Anthropic Sans&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:400;text-anchor:start;dominant-baseline:central">Secrets: AWS Secrets Manager (IAM role, auto-rotation)</text>
